title: Sim Coaster
description:
I found this impossible to find
So here you guys are

This is Sim Coaster (aka Theme Park Inc or Theme Park Manager)



File Type: MDF
Release Date: 2001
OS: Windows (i have gotten it to work in cedega/wine)
Developer: Bull Frog Inc
Publisher: EA
Mode: Single Player
Rating: ESRB E for Everyone / OFLC G

Description-
A theme Park simulator where you build you own parks while meeting challenges to expand you park, opening new rides and roller coasters in the process. One of my personal favorites, youll enjoy it if your a fan of Roller Coaster Tycoon and other such games. Graphics are fair considering its 2001, back in the days of Windows NT and ME

Mount with DAEMON Tools and install
